    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and detailed so it still has that showroom shine! It looks and drives like it's brand new, with not a single scratch to be found. If you're looking for something that's been loved and cared for perfectly, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
