    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six producing 385 hp and 310 lb-ft of torque. This specimen is equipped with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle and the factory Sport Chrono Package, allowing for sharpened throttle mapping and increased PSM thresholds. The chassis benefits from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) with a 10mm lower ride height, ensuring exceptional lateral stability and turn-in precision. Meticulously preserved, the vehicle shows zero evidence of bore scoring or oil seepage, with a dry undercarriage and a flawless DME overrev report. Every bushing, seal, and heat shield remains in factory-fresh condition, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule and climate-controlled storage. This is a definitive collector-quality example for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
